```python
def replace_values(obj, target_types=(type(None),), replacement="", handle_lists=True):
    if isinstance(obj, dict):
        return {k: replace_values(v, target_types, replacement, handle_lists) for k, v in obj.items()}
    if handle_lists and isinstance(obj, list):
        return [replace_values(item, target_types, replacement, handle_lists) for item in obj]
    if isinstance(obj, target_types):
        return replacement
    return obj
```

用法：

